{"tid":1756024,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"又話本土第一？","createTime":"2019-11-26T00:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T00:52:28.000Z","uid":129438,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bd9ee072dd2679c3f8b5ac928bedc8600552f469","tid":1756024,"uid":129438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:52:28.000Z","msg":"我就係呢區既選民，其實九龍城區咁藍既區有得贏都已經偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />結果見到傳統泛民都有成三千幾票，但政綱係五大訴求既3號竟然得幾十票。我睇到真係好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然睇住個結果係贏咗，但係我真係好希望見到大家真係本土行先，冇得揀先要含淚投泛民，而唔係得個講字。<br />\n<br />\n利申:唔係特別幫住3號，係只要邊個政綱講光復香港時代革命，五大訴求，我都會即刻投佢。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xW1zeyF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxW1zeyF.png&h=92d12150&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yMEXWM1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyMEXWM1.png&h=c174d715&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}